{"tid":1167061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔村屋散燶味　揭男子生意失敗燒炭喪命","createTime":"2019-05-22T23:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T02:38:44.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4f5e307059b74dfd9cae1979d488ba28e89781c3","tid":1167061,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T23:33:34.000Z","msg":"昨日(23日)晚上9時31分，警方接獲一名41歲姓廖女村民報案，指在大埔錦石新村75-76號一單位，發現有燒燶物件氣味散出。救援人員到場破門入屋，發現43歲姓鄧男子倒斃於單位書房內，身旁有一盤燒過的炭，警員封鎖現場調查，並檢獲遺書，相信事件並無可疑，正聯絡死者家人協助調查。 <br />\n<br />\n消息指，男事主因生意失敗而燒炭尋死。 <br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線： <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222 <br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000 <br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288 <br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000 <br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281 <br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350 <br />\n利民會： 3512 2626 <br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=876f4662\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190523/mobile/bkn-20190523032825607-0523_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190523%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190523032825607-0523_00822_001.html&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=b89258c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190523/mobile/bkn-20190523032825607-0523_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d393946749fbc069fa24674b210b107dfe696075","tid":1167061,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T23:39:36.000Z","msg":"印度佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dedd039e04cedda127b08201a97cfa22abfc4520","tid":1167061,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T02:30:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"326b872bb9a56bc77c666ec3554225775d553787","tid":1167061,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci